Shield is a term used by Mecha to express _theme_ in other CMS.

> **Info:** This class is located in `lot\extend\shield\engine\kernel` folder.

[[e]]
echo "### Methods\n";
foreach (glob(PAGE . DS . $url->path . DS . '*.page') as $v) {
    $n = basename($v, '.page');
    if ($n === '$') continue;
    $v = Page::open($v);
    echo "\n - [" . $v->title . '](' . $v->url . ')';
}
[[/e]]